---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
import { site } from '../../data/site';
---

<Layout
  title="Moving to Eastern Idaho — New Construction Homes | Odyssey"
  description="Relocating to Eastern Idaho? Odyssey Homes builds new construction across Idaho Falls, Ammon, Rigby, Rexburg, Shelley, and Blackfoot. Here's what you need to know."
>
  <Header />

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-odyssey-charcoal text-odyssey-cream">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-odyssey-accent-light uppercase">Relocation Guide</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
        Moving to Eastern Idaho? A New Construction Builder's Guide.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg lg:text-xl text-odyssey-cream/85 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        A good portion of our buyers are coming from out of state. Different climate, different cost of living, different rhythm to life. Here's the honest version of what you'll find — and how building a new home from a distance actually works.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro callout -->
  <section class="bg-odyssey-bone border-b border-odyssey-stone/15">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 text-center">
      <p class="text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
        We're a new-construction-only builder. If you're relocating and want a brand-new home that's truly yours from foundation up, you're in the right place. If you're looking for a remodel or fixer-upper, this isn't the page for you — but we can point you to good local remodelers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The six cities -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-24">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-odyssey-accent uppercase">The Six Cities We Build In</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-odyssey-charcoal max-w-3xl">
        Eastern Idaho isn't one place. Pick the one that fits.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Most newcomers say "Idaho Falls" to mean the whole region, but our service area covers six distinct cities — each with its own feel, school district, and price points. Here's the short version of what makes each one different.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <div class="bg-odyssey-bone rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Idaho Falls</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            The hub — biggest city in Eastern Idaho, where most regional shopping, hospitals, and dining live. Home to Idaho National Laboratory (the area's largest employer), the Snake River greenbelt downtown, and the strongest job market in the region. If you're working remote but want amenities five minutes away, Idaho Falls is the obvious pick.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-odyssey-bone rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Ammon</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Idaho Falls' bedroom community — and home to our Hawks Landing and Granite Creek communities. Newer subdivisions, larger lots, and the Bonneville 93 school district (regularly one of the higher-rated districts in the state). Most of our new construction lives here.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-odyssey-bone rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Rigby</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Small-town north of Idaho Falls — slower pace, more land, well water + septic still common on rural lots. Jefferson School District 251. Big draw for families who want their kids to grow up with elbow room without giving up a 15-minute commute to Idaho Falls.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-odyssey-bone rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Rexburg</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            College town built around BYU-Idaho. Heavy LDS community influence, young demographics, and an unusually high concentration of families. Madison School District 321. If you've got connections to the university or want a values-aligned community, Rexburg is its own world — and growing fast.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-odyssey-bone rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Shelley</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            South of Idaho Falls — farming country with growing residential pockets. Tight-knit, "everyone-knows-everyone" small town feel. Shelley School District 60. Our The Parks community lives here. Good fit for buyers who want a quiet base with quick access to Idaho Falls amenities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-odyssey-bone rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Blackfoot</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Between Idaho Falls and Pocatello — the heart of Idaho's potato country and home to the Eastern Idaho State Fair. Blackfoot School District 55. More affordable than Idaho Falls or Ammon, often the right pick for buyers stretching budget while still wanting new construction.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Building from out of state -->
  <section class="bg-odyssey-bone">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-24">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-odyssey-accent uppercase">The Out-of-State Build Process</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-odyssey-charcoal max-w-3xl">
        How building works when you can't be on-site every week.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Roughly a quarter of our buyers are relocating from Utah, California, Washington, Texas, or further. We've built a process that handles distance without sacrificing quality. Here's how it goes.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[80px,1fr] gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-odyssey-accent">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">First conversation — video, not in person</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
              We start with a Zoom call to walk through your timeline, budget, and what you're looking for. No pressure to visit — we'll show you the area through screenshare and answer the questions that brochures can't. Our Project Consultants do this all the time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[80px,1fr] gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-odyssey-accent">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Virtual lot and plan selection</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
              Plat maps, drone footage, walkthrough videos of any active builds in the community. Our estimator tool lets you build out a configuration with full pricing from your couch — every floor plan, every upgrade, every finish line-itemed. By the time you fly out to sign, you already know exactly what you're buying.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[80px,1fr] gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-odyssey-accent">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Digital selections + signoffs</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
              Cabinet style, countertop slab, flooring, lighting, fixtures — all captured in our online client portal. You see what we'd recommend, you approve or change it, you sign off. No "wait, what did we pick for the powder bath?" three months in.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[80px,1fr] gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-odyssey-accent">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Weekly progress updates with photos</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
              You get a build-chat group with your superintendent, project consultant, and the rest of our team. Photos every Friday at minimum. FaceTime walkthroughs whenever you want one. If something needs a decision, we ping you with options and timestamps, not abstract questions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[80px,1fr] gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-odyssey-accent">5</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Walkthrough and close</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
              When the house is finished, we do a final walkthrough — in person if you can fly out, virtual if you can't. Closing happens with mobile notaries and title companies set up to handle out-of-state buyers. The keys are in your hand the day you arrive.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Cost of living -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-24">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-odyssey-accent uppercase">Cost of Living</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-odyssey-charcoal max-w-3xl">
        Your dollar goes further than you think.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Eastern Idaho isn't the cheapest market in the country anymore — prices climbed considerably between 2020 and 2025 — but compared to California, the Pacific Northwest, the Front Range, or any major metro, you'll find:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-odyssey-accent font-bold">•</span><span><strong>No state sales tax on groceries above the basic exemption.</strong> Idaho has a 6% sales tax that applies broadly, but tax burden overall ranks among the lower 25 states.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-odyssey-accent font-bold">•</span><span><strong>State income tax is a flat 5.8%</strong> — simpler and lower than California (up to 13.3%) or Oregon (up to 9.9%).</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-odyssey-accent font-bold">•</span><span><strong>Property tax on a $500K home runs roughly $3,500-$4,500/year</strong> in most Eastern Idaho counties — well below comparable West Coast metros.</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-odyssey-accent font-bold">•</span><span><strong>Utility costs are among the lowest in the country</strong> (Idaho Power keeps electricity rates near the bottom nationally; natural gas is similarly cheap).</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-odyssey-accent font-bold">•</span><span><strong>Lot sizes are generous</strong> — most of our new construction sits on 1/3 to 1+ acre, often for what gets you a townhouse footprint in coastal markets.</span></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-6 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Translated: a $450K new construction Odyssey home with 3-car garage and finished basement in Ammon would price out at $900K+ in coastal Washington or California for less square footage and a smaller lot. That math is why so many of our buyers come from out of state.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Eastern Idaho over Boise -->
  <section class="bg-odyssey-bone">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-24">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] text-odyssey-accent uppercase">Eastern Idaho vs. Boise</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-odyssey-charcoal max-w-3xl">
        "Idaho" doesn't have to mean Boise.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Most national press about Idaho focuses on the Treasure Valley — Boise, Meridian, Nampa. That market is also the most expensive, most crowded, and most over-populated by 2020-2022 transplants. Eastern Idaho is a different conversation:
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Half the price, half the traffic</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Median home prices in Eastern Idaho run roughly 40-50% below Boise area equivalents. Commutes are 10-15 minutes, not 45. The growth here is real but it's a fraction of what Treasure Valley absorbed.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Stronger local identity</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Eastern Idaho retained more of its agricultural, small-town character. Tighter community feel. Less culture-war noise. If your reason for moving to Idaho was "I want to live somewhere that feels like Idaho," this is that place.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Yellowstone is in your backyard</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Idaho Falls is 90 minutes from West Yellowstone — closer than Bozeman or Jackson. Grand Teton, Sun Valley, Big Sky, Jackson Hole — all reachable for a weekend. Skiing at Grand Targhee, Kelly Canyon, or Pebble Creek without the resort-town crowds.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded p-7">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal">Real economy, not just remote workers</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
            Idaho National Laboratory, Eastern Idaho Regional Medical Center, BYU-Idaho, agriculture, construction trades. Not a region propped up entirely by transplants and tech money — which means it's more resilient to the next downturn.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA + form -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 lg:py-32 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-odyssey-accent">Start the conversation</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold text-odyssey-charcoal tracking-tight">
          Tell us about your move.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-odyssey-stone-dark leading-relaxed">
          We'll set up a video call with one of our Project Consultants, walk through what you're looking for, and tell you honestly whether Odyssey is the right builder for your situation. No hard sell — most of our out-of-state buyers take 3-6 months from first call to breaking ground.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-odyssey-stone">Phone</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-odyssey-stone-dark"><a href={site.phoneHref} class="hover:text-odyssey-accent">{site.phone}</a></p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-odyssey-stone">Email</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-odyssey-stone-dark"><a href={site.emailHref} class="hover:text-odyssey-accent">{site.email}</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <ContactForm
          heading="Get the conversation started"
          intro="Select 'Moving here from out of state' below — we'll route your message to the consultant who works with the most out-of-area buyers."
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
